TITLE: CS:S Map - Surf Map
AUTHOR: Napoleon_Dynamite
E-MAIL: matty19908@hotmail.com

FILENAME: surf_ndak47.bsp
FILESIZE: 2.11 MB
DATE RELEASED: 18 December 2005

CREDITS: everyone who joined my server whilst i was testing the map (thank you). and thanks for giving me praise :D

DESCRIPTION: this map is a surf map. how to surf: when on the ramp if your on the left press and hold D, if your on the right hold A, and never EVER press W (makes you fall), use the mouse to aim yourself. and press S to stop  in midair or on the ramp.

BUGS: i have currently found no bugs, email me if you find any.

COMMENTS: i hope you enjoy this map as much as i enjoyed making it.

Required items: counter strike source.
